21.3 4. The Simpsons KTTV 21.2 5. Frasier KNBC 20.3 6. Coach KABC 18.1 7. Home 
Improvement KABC 18.0 8. "Breathing Lessons" KCBS 17.6 9. Wings KNBC 17.2 10. 
