<TEXT>
<P>
 The company said Tuesday that its chairman, Timothy M. Aitken, has replaced 
Victor Chaltiel as president and chief executive. Chaltiel remains on the board 
of directors, but the Costa Mesa company said that his role with Abbey is under 
discussion. 
