<DOCNO> LA020994-0199 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 011842 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 9, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
